[[File:Laserscalpel.jpg|thumb|196px|A laser scalpel]]
A '''laser scalpel''' was a [[Laser/Legends|laser]]-based surgical tool, and could be used to make highly accurate incisions. At [[Republic Mobile Surgical Unit/Legends|Rimsoo]] units, laser scalpels were used for a variety of surgeries.

The [[servogrip]] pinchers on [[2-1B surgical droid/Legends|2-1B surgical droids]] were gentle enough to manipulate a laser scalpel. [[IT-O interrogation droid/Legends|IT-0 interrogation droids]] were equipped with laser scalpels.<ref name="EGTD">''[[The Essential Guide to Droids]]''</ref>

[[Ton Phanan]] of [[Wraith Squadron]] carried a laser scalpel as a holdout weapon. The model he used was almost indistinguishable from a writing implement when deactivated. This made it easily missed during a weapons search, and he could use his medical credentials as justification for carrying it if discovered. Phanan used it to deadly effect against a false [[New Republic Military Police|military police]] officer during a kidnapping attempt on the Wraiths in [[7 ABY/Legends|7 ABY]].<ref name="X-Wing: Iron Fist">''[[X-Wing: Iron Fist]]''</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
It is not clear whether or not the [[fine-point laser cutter]] was identical to the laser scalpel, or represented a distinctly different piece of equipment.

